{"photo": {"people": {"haspeople": 0}, "dateuploaded": "1352321640", "originalformat": "jpg", "owner": {"username": "Het Nieuwe Instituut - Architecture Collection", "realname": "Het Nieuwe Instituut", "nsid": "47154409@N06", "iconserver": "5497", "location": "", "path_alias": "nai_collection", "iconfarm": 6}, "publiceditability": {"canaddmeta": 1, "cancomment": 1}, "id": "8157210062", "title": {"_content": "Cit\u00e8 Industrielle"}, "media": "photo", "tags": {"tag": [{"raw": "Architecture", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-1174", "_content": "architecture", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Urban design", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-41445", "_content": "urbandesign", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Architectuur", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-86016", "_content": "architectuur", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Stedenbouw", "machine_tag": false, "id": "47109087-8157210062-559345", "_content": "stedenbouw", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Gezondheid", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-882879", "_content": "gezondheid", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Health", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-13028", "_content": "health", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Volksgezondheid", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-3100141", "_content": "volksgezondheid", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "NAi", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-65012", "_content": "nai", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Collectie", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-57858", "_content": "collectie", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Collection", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-11555", "_content": "collection", "author": "47154409@N06"}, {"raw": "Then/Now", "machine_tag": 0, "id": "47109087-8157210062-188371", "_content": "thennow", "author": "47154409@N06"}]}, "comments": {"_content": "0"}, "secret": "04ddf1c98c", "usage": {"canblog": 0, "canshare": 1, "candownload": 1, "canprint": 0}, "description": {"_content": "<b>T. Garnier. Cit\u00e9 Industrielle, Lyon, 1899-1917.</b> \n\nDe Cit\u00e9 Industrielle is een hygi\u00ebnistische en sociaalutopische stad die vanwege de rigide functiescheiding van grote invloed is geweest op belangrijke vakinhoudelijke congresbijeenkomsten waar architecten en stedenbouwkundigen met elkaar van gedachten wisselden: de Congr\u00e8s Internationaux d\u2019Architecture Moderne (CIAM 1928-1959). Le Corbusier bejubelde de Cit\u00e9 in het tijdschrift L\u2019Esprit Nouveau (1921) als prototype van de functionele stad, waarin de scheiding van functies de volksgezondheid bevorderde.\n\n<b>T. Garnier. Cit\u00e9 Industrielle, Lyon, 1899-1917.</b> \n\nThe Cit\u00e9 Industrielle is a hygienic, socially utopian city that was highly influential at important expert gatherings where architects and town planners shared ideas, such as the Congr\u00e8s Internationaux d\u2019Architecture Moderne (CIAM, 1928-1959), because of its strict separation of functions. Le Corbusier applauded the Cit\u00e9 in the periodical L\u2019Esprit Nouveau (1921) as a prototype for the functional city, where the separation of functions fostered public health."}, "isfavorite": 0, "views": "1815", "farm": 9, "visibility": {"isfriend": 0, "isfamily": 0, "ispublic": 1}, "rotation": 0, "dates": {"taken": "2012-10-31 11:57:15", "lastupdate": "1386988673", "takengranularity": "0", "posted": "1352321640"}, "originalsecret": "d052981755", "license": "7", "notes": {"note": []}, "server": "8068", "safety_level": "0", "urls": {"url": [{"type": "photopage", "_content": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/nai_collection/8157210062/"}]}, "editability": {"canaddmeta": 0, "cancomment": 0}}, "stat": "ok", "flarchive:created": 1387636258}